---
title: Trick-or-Thyme-Roasted Chicken with Spinach Guts and Crispy Potatoes
description: You know it’s going to be a good night when almost everything gets cooked right on baking sheets. In fact, all you have to do while the chicken and potatoes are baking away is sauté some spinach, which takes... get ready for it... less than five minutes.
